        <abstract> 
<p>CD gratified that ED wants to translate his <hi rend="italic">Journal</hi>. Will send a copy of <hi rend="italic">Coral reefs</hi>, which contains a fuller treatment of topic. Perhaps ED would insert a note to this effect. Can lend woodcuts from <hi rend="italic">Coral reefs</hi> if ED wants. CD will send a few corrections; he wants to amend way he criticised Agassiz’s glacier theory.</p> 
            <p>He is also enclosing a questionnaire concerning differences between races or varieties and species, about which he intends to publish sometime.</p>
        </abstract>
